            "title": "A股窄幅偏軟",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股近平開後個別發展，窄幅偏軟。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指開報3830，跌1點或0.03%，現報3829，跌1點或0.01%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指開報13074，跌1點或0.001%，現報13078，升3點或0.06%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300開報4499點，升1點或0.02%，現報4501，升3點或0.09%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數開報3098，升3點或0.1%，現報3104，升9點或0.37%。</p>\n</div>",
